<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="59" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,151,1364]" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,800,824]" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species is dimorphic with regard to the color of the forewings: some specimens have the tegmina entirely black, whereas others have the basal third of the tegmina red and the distal region black.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[199,1366,871,896]" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,151,1364]" box="[199,1366,871,896]" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">
